    <description>Leila Molana-Allen is a freelance visual journalist based in Beirut. Formerly with the Economist in London, she now focuses on social instability in conflict zones, displacement and women’s rights across the Middle East, Eastern Europe and Africa. You can follow her work on Instagram and Twitter @leila_ma.
